INSERT INTO `featured` (`pkey`, `applicationcode`, `applicationname`, `minortxt`, `majortxt`, `minorimg`, `linktxt`, `linkurl`) VALUES (1,'2001','End to End Seaming','','Merrow is the industry leader in the production of end-to-end seaming machines. These machines are used in thousands of textile finishing plants worldwide to reduce costs and allow for continuous fabric processing.  We produce many unique end-to-end seaming machines guaranteed to work with all types and weights of fabrics.','images/featured/endtoendseaming-239x200.jpg','Machines for this application.','view.jsp?sel=offendtoendfeatured'),(2,'2002','Napkins','','Merrow napkin-edging machines produce a fine rolled edge perfect for table linens such as tablecloths, napkins, and placemats.  This narrow rolled overlock edge provides added strength and style.  In addition, these machines are frequently used to create a neat edge on fabric samples in order to present the fabrics as attractively as possible.  ','images/featured/napkins-239x200.jpg','Machines for this application.','view.jsp?sel=offnapkinsfeatured'),(3,'2003','Netting','','Merrow’s netting machines are specially designed to sew a reinforced edge on netting used for a wide variety of applications, from sports equipment to safety nets.  Merrow netting machines can also reinforce net products by stitching rope or tape into the seam. No net is properly finished unless it’s finished with a Merrow edge. ','images/featured/netting-239x200.jpg','Machines for this application.','view.jsp?sel=offnettingfeatured'),(4,'2004','Emblem','','Merrow emblem-edging machines are designed to reinforce and seal the edges of embroidered emblems.  Merrow’s original emblem-edging machine, the MG-3U, is a high-speed precision machine for edging any size and shape of emblem.  Merrow has also developed something truly unique – an automated version of this machine, designed with full automation to run without an operator.  ','images/featured/emblem-239x200.jpg','Machines for this application.','view.jsp?sel=offemblemfeatured'),(5,'2005','Toe Closing','','Merrow’s unique hosiery machines were designed to create a durable overlock stitch for toe-closing.  This stitch is strong enough to produce a durable finished product, yet thin enough for comfort.  Merrow makes two unique toe-closing machines to work with all weights of fabrics.','images/featured/toeclosing-239x200.jpg','Machines for this application.','view.jsp?sel=offtoeclosingfeatured'),(6,'2006','Auto Edge Machine','','The Merrow Optical Auto-Edge Machine (MG3U AEM) is the only machine in the world of its kind: a completely automated machine for edging emblems.  Loaded with unedged emblems, the MG3U AEM can run with minimal operator input, edging 350 to 600 emblems an hour, depending on emblem size.  This machine can be reloaded while the machine is running, allowing for uninterrupted productivity.  One operator can oversee up to four machines at a time, benefiting your plant with huge savings of time and money.<br />A truly unique machine with unparalleled performance!','images/featured/autoedgemachine-239x200.jpg','Machines for this application.','view.jsp?sel=offautoedgefeatured');
