INSERT INTO `tracker` (`pkey`, `child`, `parent`, `category`, `position`, `url`, `isfinal`, `minortxt`, `minorimg`, `majortxt`, `majorimg`) VALUES (1,'Products','Home','offmain',NULL,'view.jsp?sel=offproducts',0,'','images/products/products-239x200.jpg','Merrow produces the highest-quality products for industrial sewing available anywhere, engineered for precision and reliability. Our classic innovations remain on the cutting edge of sewing technology and consistently outperform all other machines on the market.','images/products/products-239x200.jpg'),(2,'Support','Home','offmain',NULL,'',NULL,'','images/support/support-145x121.jpg','Two values set Merrow apart from other sewing machine companies: our quality, and our customer support. When you purchase a Merrow machine, you can rest assured that your machine will be supported through our guaranteed service and repairs, replacement parts, and the technical information you need. Merrow machines can be serviced through one of our thousands of licensed dealers throughout the world. With Merrow, your purchase is just the beginning - we guarantee to support your machine for as long as you can use it!','images/support/support-239x200.jpg'),(3,'About','Home','offmain',NULL,'',NULL,'','images/merrow/aboutus-145x68.jpg','Merrow is a unique type of company producing one-of-a-kind, high-quality products for the textile and apparel industries. Merrow represents quality, service, and ambition ? an ambition to accomplish nothing less than the reinvention of the American textile industry. What sets Merrow apart are our people, our history and our vision. These things make a difference that is apparent in everything we do. Take a closer look -','images/merrow/aboutus-239x200.jpg'),(4,'Accounts','Home','offmain',NULL,'',NULL,'','images/accounts/accounts-145x68.jpg','','images/accounts/accounts-239x200.jpg'),(5,'Merrow Design','Home','offmain',NULL,'',NULL,'','images/design/merrowdesign-145x68.jpg','','images/design/merrowdesign-239x200.jpg'),(6,'Netting Machines','Home','offmain',NULL,'',NULL,'','images/featured/nettingmachines-145x68.jpg','','images/featured/nettingmachines-239x200.jpg'),(7,'Textile Finishing','Home','offmain',NULL,'',NULL,'','images/featured/textilefinishing-145x68.jpg','','images/featured/textilefinishing-239x200.jpg'),(8,'Financials','Advertisement','offrandom',1,'random.jsp?code=5001',1,'','images/random/financials-145x68.jpg','','images/random/financials-239x200.jpg'),(9,'Merry Christmas','Advertisement','offrandom',2,'random.jsp?code=5002',1,'','images/random/merrychristmas-145x68.jpg','','images/random/merrychristmas-239x200.jpg'),(10,'70-D3-B2-123 Launch','Advertisement','offrandom',3,'random.jsp?code=5003',1,'','images/random/70-D3-B2-123launch-145x68.jpg','','images/random/70-D3-B2-123launch-239x200.jpg'),(12,'Leadership','About','offmerrow',3,'ourteam.jsp',1,'','images/merrow/ourteam-145x121.jpg','','images/merrow/ourteam-239x200.jpg'),(13,'Our Vision','About','offmerrow',2,'aboutus.jsp',1,'','images/merrow/ourvision-145x121.jpg','','images/merrow/ourvision-239x200.jpg'),(14,'Contact Us','About','offmerrow',1,'contactus.jsp',1,'','images/merrow/contactus-145x121.jpg','','images/merrow/contactus-239x200.jpg'),(15,'Our History','About','offmerrow',4,'ourhistory.jsp',1,'','images/merrow/ourhistory-145x121.jpg','','images/merrow/ourhistory-239x200.jpg'),(16,'Careers','About','offmerrow',5,'view.jsp?sel=offcareers',0,'','images/careers/careers-145x121.jpg','Merrow is an exciting and challenging place to work.  We are driven not by a corporate structure, but by brains, innovation and imagination.  As Merrow continues to grow, we are continually looking for new people to join our team.  Think you would like to work for Merrow?  Please look over our current job postings.\r\nMerrow is an equal-opportunity employer.','images/careers/careers-239x200.jpg'),(17,'Merrow @ The World','About','(offmerrow)',6,'merrowworld.jsp',1,'','images/faqs/faq1.jpeg','Charley:\r\n \r\nGood afternoon!\r\n \r\nI revert to our telephone conversation yesterday regarding requqest from Gildan Choloma Textiles S.A., to present them with a quotation for the following machines:\r\n \r\n12 sets Merrow heads Model 70D3B2CNP, 1-needle 1-thread butt seam machine, WITH MODIFIED THROAT PLATE HAVING NARROWER STITCH TONGUE ( STANDARD THROAT PLATE  HAS 14 MMS. WIDTH AT STITCH TONGUE ( IN LINE OF NEEDLE PENETRATION IN THROAT PLATE ).-   THEY REQUIRE 11 MMS. STITCH TONGUE WIDTH AT RIGHT SIDE OF NEEDLE PENETRATION LINE ).-\r\nIf any modification needs to be done on stitch finger on presser foot, O.K.\r\n \r\n11 sets Merrow heads Model 70D3B2, with same modification on throat plate as above.-  If narrowing the throat plate stitch tongue requires also a modification on stitch finger on presser foot, o.k.\r\n \r\nI would like to know if you could send us one (1) throat plate with above measurements, to try at one of Gildan\'s machines, to finalize this testing, and also, advise if there is any difference in costs for additional plating needed, etc.  You may ship  immediately to our Miami address as follows:\r\n \r\nAGENCIA J.E.HANDAL S.A. DE C.V.\r\n2227 N.W. 79TH. AVEN.\r\nDORAL, FL. 33122\r\nUSA\r\nTEL: (305) 433-7007\r\n \r\nI wait your reply a.s.a.p.\r\n \r\nBest regards','images/faqs/faq2.gif'),(18,'Dealer Locator','Home','offmain',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(19,'Forums/Blogs','Support','(offsupport)',5,'blog.jsp',1,'','images/blog/blog-145x68.jpg','','images/blog/blog-239x200.jpg'),(20,'FAQ\'s','Support','offsupport',4,'view.jsp?sel=offfaq',0,'','images/support/faq-145x121.jpg','','images/support/faq-239x200.jpg'),(21,'Parts Manuals','Support','offsupport',3,'view.jsp?sel=offpartmanual',0,'','images/support/partsmanual-145x121.jpg','','images/support/partsmanual-239x200.jpg'),(22,'Technical Manuals','Support','offsupport',2,'techmanuals.jsp',1,'','images/support/technicalmanuals-145x121.jpg','Merrow?s online technical manuals ease the process of operating and servicing your Merrow machine.  Please consult our online manuals for troubleshooting advice.  If you have any further questions, call Merrow at 508.295.8899.','images/support/technicalmanuals-239x200.jpg'),(23,'Custom Stitch Samples','Support','offsupport',1,'askmerrow.jsp',1,'Send us your fabric, we send you a stitch sample.','images/support/askmerrow-145x121.jpg','','images/support/askmerrow-239x200.jpg'),(24,'Press','About','(offmerrow)',8,'view.jsp?sel=offpress',0,'','images/merrow/press-145x68.jpg','','images/merrow/press-239x200.jpg'),(26,'End to End Seaming','Featured Applications','offfeatured',1,'showfeatured.jsp?code=2001',1,'','images/featured/endtoend-145x68.jpg','Merrow is the industry leader in the production of end-to-end seaming machines. These machines are used in thousands of textile finishing plants worldwide to reduce costs and allow for continuous fabric processing.  We produce many unique end-to-end seaming machines guaranteed to work with all types and weights of fabrics.','images/featured/endtoend-239x200.jpg'),(27,'Napkins','Featured Applications','offfeatured',2,'showfeatured.jsp?code=2002',1,'','images/featured/napkins-145x68.jpg','Merrow napkin-edging machines produce a fine rolled edge perfect for table linens such as tablecloths, napkins, and placemats.  This narrow rolled overlock edge provides added strength and style.  In addition, these machines are frequently used to create a neat edge on fabric samples in order to present the fabrics as attractively as possible.','images/featured/napkins-239x200.jpg'),(28,'Netting','Featured Applications','offfeatured',3,'showfeatured.jsp?code=2003',1,'','images/featured/netting-145x68.jpg','Merrow?s netting machines are specially designed to sew a reinforced edge on netting used for a wide variety of applications, from sports equipment to safety nets.  Merrow netting machines can also reinforce net products by stitching rope or tape into the seam. No net is properly finished unless it?s finished with a Merrow edge. ','images/featured/netting-239x200.jpg'),(29,'Emblem','Featured Applications','offfeatured',4,'showfeatured.jsp?code=2004',1,'','images/featured/emblem-145x68.jpg','Merrow emblem-edging machines are designed to reinforce and seal the edges of embroidered emblems.  Merrow?s original emblem-edging machine, the MG-3U, is a high-speed precision machine for edging any size and shape of emblem.  Merrow has also developed something truly unique ? an automated version of this machine, designed with full automation to run without an operator.  ','images/featured/emblem-239x200.jpg'),(30,'Toe Closing','Featured Applications','offfeatured',5,'showfeatured.jsp?code=2005',1,'','images/featured/toeclosing-145x68.jpg','Merrow?s unique hosiery machines were designed to create a durable overlock stitch for toe-closing.  This stitch is strong enough to produce a durable finished product, yet thin enough for comfort.  Merrow makes two unique toe-closing machines to work with all weights of fabrics.','images/featured/toeclosing-239x200.jpg'),(31,'Machines','Products','offproducts',1,'view.jsp?sel=offmachines',0,'With over 75 models of overlock sewing machines for a range of purposes, Merrow is the industry leader for quality and reliability.','images/products/machines-145x121.jpg','Merrow is the only manufacturer in the world producing cam-driven sewing machines that stand up to heavy-duty use. Our cam-driven machines produce a superior-quality stitch that is the most precise in the industry. \r\nMerrow machines are hand-built from the highest quality precision parts. Top-quality engineering insures that your machine will run reliably for decades ? up to sixty years in the factory environment. \r\nQuality engineering, quality parts and quality production ? these are the traits that set Merrow machines apart.','images/products/machines-239x200.jpg'),(32,'Parts','Products','offproducts',4,'showpartproduct.jsp?code=',1,'The highest quality parts, made in the USA and pre